'''Ug''' is a children's book by [[Raymond Briggs]]. In 2001 it won the [[Nestl<U+00E9> Smarties Book Prize]] Silver Award.<ref>[http://www.booktrusted.co.uk/nestle/ Nestl<U+00E9> Children's Book Prize]</ref>

